						               													<description>Queens and Kings ...A Checkers Game is an abstract strategy game for 2 or 4 players that plays like checkers and in addition introduces a queen component that throws strategy out the door on each and every move. The game can be played in either two player  or team mode. &amp;#10;More about the game: The Queen, being tired of a male dominated game that either features only the King or the Queen in a lesser role, created a 2/4-player game that  shows the Queen&amp;rsquo;s ability to be the master of the game . &amp;#10;Queen and Kings ...A Checkers Game, introduces a Queen scepter in the center of the board, upon capturing it the King is introduced. The King can move one space in any direction, forward or backwards along its diagonal grid. Advancing your piece to the opposite end of the board creates a Queen that can fly diagonally across the board, seizing all opponents in her path. Both Queen and King have a strategic value, so choose wisely because once a Queen or King that  piece remains so until defeated or game is over. Each game starts with either 9  pieces that can only move forward along its diagonal grid, so be mindful of the Queen and her pursuit of her opponents &amp;#10;In Queens &amp;amp; Kings ...A Checkers Game, In Team mode it takes a coordinated effort to defeat your opponents. The 9 piece- games plays out in about 30 minutes to 90 minutes. &amp;#10;What will be your strategy? The Queen now sits next to the King on her throne and peace and harmony reigns in the kingdom, or does it?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
